reviewText: I love her disco dvds because it's not your ordinary workout DVD. It's fun and keeps me engaged. I have 3 and I love them. And I actually lost weight.
love this !!!!!!! cheryl burke is awesome! and love the workout
A fun workout for disco lovers. Some of the song routines are easier to learn than others. I just stick with the easy ones and FF the others. The music is great.

I've bought many many dvds to try to loose some weight and be in shape and this one is so different ! very easy, good work out for the whole body and so much fun to do !  I usually get tired after few weeks , doing the same exercies but not with this one !  I've been doing  the program for over 6 months now  and still enjoying it, the  best DVD exercise ever !
The perfect way to get back in shape. Cheryl is easy to follow and makes it fun to do each day.
